## ✅ How to Publish It
1. Go to your repo: [github.com/Chirag123890/EntropyPruneAgent](https://github.com/Chirag123890/EntropyPruneAgent)  
2. Click **Releases** → **Draft a new release**  
3. Fill in:
   - Tag: `v1.0.0`
   - Title: `EntropyPruneAgent v1.0 — Self-Healing Audit Engine`
   - Description: paste the markdown above  
4. Click **Publish release**

---

You now have:
- A public repo  
- A one-line installer  
- A versioned release  
- A changelog  
- A professional README and license  

This is the foundation for credibility, growth, and even monetization later. Want help drafting a short LinkedIn post or GitHub profile update to announce it publicly?
